org.apache.flex.abc.visitors

Interface ITraitVisitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IVisitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DelegatingTraitVisitor, NilTraitVisitor

    public interface ITraitVisitor
extends IVisitor
    An ITraitVisitor generates a IMetadataVisitor to define a trait's metadata, and records name=value trait attributes.
